						<p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center;">
							In today's digital world, your website is often the first impression potential customers have of your business. For {tradeName.toLowerCase()}, having a professional, mobile-friendly website is essential for growing your business.
