										<path d="M3.27 6.96 12 12.01l8.73-5.05"></path>
										<path d="M12 22.08V12"></path>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--color-navy-900); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Showcase Your Work</h3>
									<p style="color: #475569; line-height: 1.75;">Display your past projects, testimonials, and certifications to prove you're the best choice for the job.</p>
								</div>
