								</div>
								<div>
									<h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--color-navy-900); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Capture Leads 24/7</h3>
									<p style="color: #475569; line-height: 1.75;">Your website works around the clock, capturing leads even when you're on a job or unavailable.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Features Section -->
			<section style="padding: 6rem 0; background: #f8fafc;">
				<div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1rem;">
					<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
						<h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--color-navy-900); margin-bottom: 1rem;">What's Included</h2>
						<p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #475569; max-width: 42rem; margin: 0 auto;">Everything you need to get online and start generating leads.</p>
