								<div>
									<h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--color-navy-900); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Fast Loading Speed</h3>
									<p style="color: #475569; line-height: 1.75;">Lightning-fast page load times keep visitors engaged and improve your Google rankings.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div style="background: white; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
							<div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 1.5rem;">
								<div style="width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; background: var(--color-gold-500); border-radius: 0.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-navy-900);">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
										<path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path>
									</svg>
